[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":640},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fai\u002F20260622\u002F4283716095\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fai\u002F20260622\u002F4283716095\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fai\u002F20260622\u002F4283716095\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fai\u002F20260622\u002F4283716095\u002F":618,"related:\u002Fai\u002F20260622\u002F4283716095\u002F":627},"\u002Fen\u002Fai\u002F2026\u002F06\u002F22\u002Fllms-txt-cloudflare-transform-rule-markdown-content-type\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":597,"date":598,"description":599,"extension":600,"lang":601,"meta":602,"navigation":603,"path":604,"readingMinutes":605,"seo":606,"standalone":607,"stem":608,"tags":609,"tldr":615,"updated":598,"url":616,"__hash__":617},"content\u002Fai\u002F讓-gh-pages-的-llms-txt-回傳-text-markdown-Cloudflare-回應標頭轉換規則教學.md","讓 gh-pages 的 \u002Fllms.txt 回傳 text\u002Fmarkdown：Cloudflare 回應標頭轉換規則教學","4283716095",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":584},"minimark",[11,19,23,49,62,85,96,100,107,116,182,191,197,200,223,226,230,233,236,239,242,247,276,282,285,290,294,301,308,314,318,321,328,337,343,346,364,367,373,377,388,412,418,423,433,437,443,464,467,487,492,501,520,523,526,560,566,577,580],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":17,"src":18},"讓 \u002Fllms.txt 回傳 text\u002Fmarkdown：Cloudflare 回應標頭轉換規則教學","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fcloudflare-transform-rules\u002FChatGPT%20Image%202026%E5%B9%B46%E6%9C%8822%E6%97%A5%20%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8802_33_15.png",[20,21,22],"h2",{"id":22},"前言",[12,24,25,26,33,34,39,40,44,45,48],{},"之前我有寫過一篇 ",[27,28,32],"a",{"href":29,"rel":30},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fai\u002F20260408\u002F3734112946\u002F",[31],"nofollow","SEO 已經不夠了嗎？認識 AEO 答案引擎優化"," 跟 ",[27,35,38],{"href":36,"rel":37},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fai\u002F20260421\u002F2847193056\u002F",[31],"從 3 分到滿分！讓你的網站通過 isitagentready","，裡面有提到 ",[41,42,43],"code",{},"\u002Fllms.txt"," 是用來告訴 AI 搜尋引擎你的網站有哪些東西的索引檔，然後這邊有個關鍵是你必須要把它的 Content-Type 標成 ",[41,46,47],{},"text\u002Fmarkdown","。",[12,50,51,52,33,54,57,58,61],{},"那這邊我自己也乖乖把 ",[41,53,43],{},[41,55,56],{},"\u002Fllms-full.txt"," 丟到 gh-pages 上，可是如果你這時候順便 ",[41,59,60],{},"curl -I"," 一下你會發現回傳的是...",[63,64,69],"pre",{"className":65,"code":66,"language":67,"meta":68,"style":68},"language-txt shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","HTTP\u002F2 200\ncontent-type: text\u002Fplain\n","txt","",[41,70,71,79],{"__ignoreMap":68},[72,73,76],"span",{"class":74,"line":75},"line",1,[72,77,78],{},"HTTP\u002F2 200\n",[72,80,82],{"class":74,"line":81},2,[72,83,84],{},"content-type: text\u002Fplain\n",[12,86,87,88,91,92,95],{},"所以這一篇就是要來分享我怎麼用 Cloudflare 的回應標頭轉換規則，把 ",[41,89,90],{},"content-type: text\u002Fplain"," 改成 ",[41,93,94],{},"text\u002Fmarkdown; charset=utf-8","，而這整個過程不用寫 Cloudflare Worker，免費方案就夠用哩～",[20,97,99],{"id":98},"為什麼-llmstxt-會跑成-textplain","為什麼 \u002Fllms.txt 會跑成 text\u002Fplain？",[12,101,102,103,106],{},"這個問題其實很簡單，因為它的副檔名是 ",[41,104,105],{},".txt","（對，就是這樣而已）。",[12,108,109,110,115],{},"每個 web server 在回應靜態檔的時候，會根據副檔名查一張對應表（叫做 MIME 對應表）來決定 Content-Type 要寫什麼。GitHub Pages 用的是業界很通用的 ",[27,111,114],{"href":112,"rel":113},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fjshttp\u002Fmime-db",[31],"mime-db"," 那一套，對應規則大概長這樣：",[117,118,119,132],"table",{},[120,121,122],"thead",{},[123,124,125,129],"tr",{},[126,127,128],"th",{},"副檔名",[126,130,131],{},"對應的 Content-Type",[133,134,135,147,158,170],"tbody",{},[123,136,137,142],{},[138,139,140],"td",{},[41,141,105],{},[138,143,144],{},[41,145,146],{},"text\u002Fplain",[123,148,149,154],{},[138,150,151],{},[41,152,153],{},".md",[138,155,156],{},[41,157,47],{},[123,159,160,165],{},[138,161,162],{},[41,163,164],{},".html",[138,166,167],{},[41,168,169],{},"text\u002Fhtml",[123,171,172,177],{},[138,173,174],{},[41,175,176],{},".xml",[138,178,179],{},[41,180,181],{},"application\u002Fxml",[12,183,184,185,187,188,190],{},"所以 ",[41,186,105],{}," 結尾的檔案就會被標注成 ",[41,189,146],{},"，即使你裡面寫的是 markdown 格式，web server 也不會幫你看內容，它只認副檔名。",[12,192,193,194,196],{},"這時候應該又有一個疑問了：",[41,195,146],{}," AI 還是讀得到啊，反正內容是 markdown，給它讀就好不是嗎？",[12,198,199],{},"對，AI 確實還是讀得到，可是這邊有兩個小問題：",[201,202,203,214],"ol",{},[204,205,206,210,211,213],"li",{},[207,208,209],"strong",{},"少了明確的格式信號："," AI 拿到 ",[41,212,146],{}," 之後會把它當純文字處理，不一定會啟動 markdown 的解析邏輯，這導致標題、列表、連結這些結構就比較容易被當成一般文字看待，那就沒辦法發揮 markdown 格式的優勢了。",[204,215,216,219,220,222],{},[207,217,218],{},"有些工具會看 Content-Type 決定要不要拿："," 像 Anthropic、OpenAI 的文件裡都有提到，建議站點在提供 markdown 內容時把 Content-Type 標成 ",[41,221,47],{},"，這樣 AI Agent 看到的時候會更明確知道這是要給它看的 markdown 內容，會比較友善地把它當成 markdown 來處理。",[12,224,225],{},"所以 Content-Type 的調整就變得格外重要。",[20,227,229],{"id":228},"為什麼選-cloudflare-回應標頭轉換規則","為什麼選 Cloudflare 回應標頭轉換規則？",[12,231,232],{},"我認為對「就只是想改 Content-Type」這種相對單純的需求來講，用 Cloudflare 的回應標頭轉換規則最簡單，更不用說我自己的網域本來就是託管在 Cloudflare 上（畢竟 gh-pages 本身也沒有地方讓你動 header）。",[12,234,235],{},"所以接下來，就來介紹一下該如何設定吧。",[20,237,238],{"id":238},"設定步驟",[12,240,241],{},"整個流程非常簡單，只需要幾分鐘就可以設定完了。",[243,244,246],"h3",{"id":245},"step-1進到轉換規則頁面","Step 1：進到轉換規則頁面",[201,248,249,257,260,266],{},[204,250,251,252],{},"登入 ",[27,253,256],{"href":254,"rel":255},"https:\u002F\u002Fdash.cloudflare.com\u002F",[31],"Cloudflare Dashboard",[204,258,259],{},"選你要設定的網域（這邊以我的部落格 israynotarray.com 為例）",[204,261,262,263],{},"左側選單點 ",[207,264,265],{},"規則 → 轉換規則",[204,267,268,269,272,273],{},"找到 ",[207,270,271],{},"回應標頭轉換規則"," 那一欄，點右上角 ",[207,274,275],{},"建立規則",[12,277,278],{},[15,279],{"alt":280,"src":281},"轉換規則頁面","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fcloudflare-transform-rules\u002F20260622133415.png",[12,283,284],{},"這邊選擇「回應標頭轉換規則」",[12,286,287],{},[15,288],{"alt":275,"src":289},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fcloudflare-transform-rules\u002F20260622133425.png",[243,291,293],{"id":292},"step-2填規則名稱","Step 2：填規則名稱",[12,295,296,297,300],{},"規則名稱我這邊取 ",[41,298,299],{},"Set markdown content-type","，方便我之後一眼看出來這個規則在幹嘛。",[12,302,303,304,307],{},"你也可以叫 ",[41,305,306],{},"llms.txt markdown header"," 之類的，反正隨你喜歡。",[12,309,310],{},[15,311],{"alt":312,"src":313},"填規則名稱","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fcloudflare-transform-rules\u002F20260622142309.png",[243,315,317],{"id":316},"step-3寫比對條件","Step 3：寫比對條件",[12,319,320],{},"接下來這邊稍微有一點坑 XD",[12,322,323,324,327],{},"所以我個人建議直接使用 ",[207,325,326],{},"編輯運算式"," 模式比較好，然後把整段貼進去：",[63,329,331],{"className":65,"code":330,"language":67,"meta":68,"style":68},"(http.request.uri.path eq \"\u002Fllms.txt\") or (http.request.uri.path eq \"\u002Fllms-full.txt\") or (ends_with(http.request.uri.path, \".md\"))\n",[41,332,333],{"__ignoreMap":68},[72,334,335],{"class":74,"line":75},[72,336,330],{},[12,338,339],{},[15,340],{"alt":341,"src":342},"貼上比對運算式","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fcloudflare-transform-rules\u002F20260622142529.png",[12,344,345],{},"這段運算式做了三件事情：",[347,348,349,354,358],"ul",{},[204,350,351,352],{},"抓 ",[41,353,43],{},[204,355,351,356],{},[41,357,56],{},[204,359,360,361,363],{},"抓所有 ",[41,362,153],{}," 結尾的檔案（如果你有開「每篇文章對應一份 .md」這種設計的話）",[12,365,366],{},"所以你的畫面按完成之後應該會變成這樣：",[12,368,369],{},[15,370],{"alt":371,"src":372},"完成後的運算式預覽","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fcloudflare-transform-rules\u002F20260622133032.png",[243,374,376],{"id":375},"step-4設定要塞的-header","Step 4：設定要塞的 header",[12,378,379,380,383,384,387],{},"接下來是最重要的一個步驟，請你往下到 ",[207,381,382],{},"則..."," 區塊，點 ",[207,385,386],{},"設定新標頭"," 按鈕，會展開三個欄位讓你填：",[347,389,390,396,405],{},[204,391,392,395],{},[207,393,394],{},"動作："," 選「設定靜態」（Set static）",[204,397,398,401,402],{},[207,399,400],{},"標頭名稱："," 填 ",[41,403,404],{},"Content-Type",[204,406,407,401,410],{},[207,408,409],{},"值：",[41,411,94],{},[12,413,414,417],{},[41,415,416],{},"charset=utf-8"," 這段建議加上去，不然中文內容在某些 client 上可能會出現編碼錯亂。",[12,419,420],{},[15,421],{"alt":404,"src":422},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fcloudflare-transform-rules\u002F20260622133158.png",[12,424,425,428,429,432],{},[207,426,427],{},"放置於"," 保持預設的「最後」就好，按右下角 ",[207,430,431],{},"部署"," 就完成啦～",[243,434,436],{"id":435},"step-5用-curl-驗證","Step 5：用 curl 驗證",[12,438,439,440,442],{},"部署完之後打開 terminal，跑一下 ",[41,441,60],{}," 看回應的 header：",[63,444,448],{"className":445,"code":446,"language":447,"meta":68,"style":68},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","curl -I https:\u002F\u002F你的網域\u002Fllms.txt\n","bash",[41,449,450],{"__ignoreMap":68},[72,451,452,456,460],{"class":74,"line":75},[72,453,455],{"class":454},"s_sBn","curl",[72,457,459],{"class":458},"sCcAr"," -I",[72,461,463],{"class":462},"sTRMh"," https:\u002F\u002F你的網域\u002Fllms.txt\n",[12,465,466],{},"預期看到的回應大概長這樣：",[63,468,470],{"className":65,"code":469,"language":67,"meta":68,"style":68},"HTTP\u002F2 200\ncontent-type: text\u002Fmarkdown; charset=utf-8\nserver: cloudflare\n",[41,471,472,476,481],{"__ignoreMap":68},[72,473,474],{"class":74,"line":75},[72,475,78],{},[72,477,478],{"class":74,"line":81},[72,479,480],{},"content-type: text\u002Fmarkdown; charset=utf-8\n",[72,482,484],{"class":74,"line":483},3,[72,485,486],{},"server: cloudflare\n",[12,488,489],{},[15,490],{"alt":455,"src":491},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fai\u002Fcloudflare-transform-rules\u002F20260622133228.png",[12,493,494,497,498,500],{},[41,495,496],{},"content-type"," 變成 ",[41,499,94],{}," 就代表規則生效了。",[502,503,504],"blockquote",{},[12,505,506,509,510,512,513,515,516,519],{},[207,507,508],{},"Note","\n如果你看到 ",[41,511,496],{}," 還是 ",[41,514,146],{},"，可能是 Cloudflare 邊緣快取還沒更新。可以加 ",[41,517,518],{},"-H \"Cache-Control: no-cache\""," 重抓一次，或者直接去 Cloudflare Dashboard 的快取頁面點「清除快取」一下。",[20,521,522],{"id":522},"結語",[12,524,525],{},"最後總結一些重點吧。",[201,527,528,537,551,554],{},[204,529,530,531,533,534,536],{},"如果部署在 gh-pages 上，",[41,532,105],{}," 結尾的檔案預設會被標成 ",[41,535,146],{},"，這時候 AI 爬蟲就不太會把它當 markdown 來處理了。",[204,538,539,540,542,543,545,546,548,549,48],{},"用 Cloudflare 的回應標頭轉換規則可以很簡單地把 ",[41,541,43],{},"、",[41,544,56],{}," 和所有 ",[41,547,153],{}," 檔的 Content-Type 改成 ",[41,550,94],{},[204,552,553],{},"設定的時候要注意比對條件的寫法，建議直接用編輯運算式的方式，這樣比較不會踩坑（要選「URI 路徑」不是「完整 URI」）。",[204,555,556,557,559],{},"設定完之後可以用 ",[41,558,60],{}," 來驗證 header 是否有正確被改寫。",[12,561,562,563,565],{},"這條規則做完之後，下次 AI 爬蟲來抓 ",[41,564,43],{}," 就會拿到明確的 markdown 格式信號。",[12,567,568,569,572,573,576],{},"那如果你想做更進階的 Markdown Negotiation（也就是 AI 帶 ",[41,570,571],{},"Accept: text\u002Fmarkdown"," header 時，把整篇 HTML 文章即時轉成 markdown 回給它），那就要動到 Cloudflare Worker 了，這部分我之前在 ",[27,574,38],{"href":36,"rel":575},[31]," 那篇有完整的 Worker 寫法可以參考。",[12,578,579],{},"到這邊整個 AEO 的最後一哩路就接起來了。希望這一篇有讓你對 Cloudflare 轉換規則有更近一步的認識哩～",[581,582,583],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}",{"title":68,"searchDepth":81,"depth":81,"links":585},[586,587,588,589,596],{"id":22,"depth":81,"text":22},{"id":98,"depth":81,"text":99},{"id":228,"depth":81,"text":229},{"id":238,"depth":81,"text":238,"children":590},[591,592,593,594,595],{"id":245,"depth":483,"text":246},{"id":292,"depth":483,"text":293},{"id":316,"depth":483,"text":317},{"id":375,"depth":483,"text":376},{"id":435,"depth":483,"text":436},{"id":522,"depth":81,"text":522},"AI","2026-06-22 14:00:00","這篇分享怎麼用 Cloudflare 的回應標頭轉換規則，一條規則就把 GitHub Pages 上的 \u002Fllms.txt、\u002Fllms-full.txt 與所有 .md 檔的 Content-Type 改回 text\u002Fmarkdown，不用另外寫 Cloudflare Worker。內容涵蓋為什麼 .txt 副檔名預設會被 mime-db 對應成 text\u002Fplain、Transform Rules 的免費方案額度（10 條）、Cloudflare Dashboard 的完整設定步驟、編輯運算式怎麼寫，以及用 curl -I 驗證的方式。","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fai\u002Fgh-pages-llms-txt-text-markdown-cloudflare","3",{"title":6,"description":599},false,"ai\u002F讓-gh-pages-的-llms-txt-回傳-text-markdown-Cloudflare-回應標頭轉換規則教學",[597,610,611,612,271,613,614,404],"AEO","Cloudflare","Cloudflare Transform Rules","llms.txt","GitHub Pages",null,"\u002Fai\u002F20260622\u002F4283716095\u002F","_GlvxpKtqJaQyVEopHJDAwYTGotN9MEJI6yC66GpF1Q",{"newer":619,"older":623},{"url":620,"title":621,"date":622},"\u002Fother\u002F20260623\u002F2826413095\u002F","Mac 系統監控工具就推薦用 Stats！一款免費又開源，還能看 CPU、GPU、溫度、網速的軟體","2026-06-23 10:00:00",{"url":624,"title":625,"date":626},"\u002Fai\u002F20260616\u002F3947261580\u002F","AI 是不是偷偷變笨了？AIStupidLevel：24 小時監測 AI 模型退化的評測網站","2026-06-16 10:00:00",[628,633,638],{"url":629,"title":630,"date":631,"readingMinutes":632},"\u002Fai\u002F20260629\u002F2995176290\u002F","新版 Claude Code 終端機攔截滑鼠點擊超煩！用 CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_MOUSE_CLICKS 環境變數把它關掉","2026-06-29 18:00:00","2",{"url":634,"title":635,"date":636,"readingMinutes":637},"\u002Fai\u002F20260627\u002F1947382651\u002F","design.md？如果你使用 AI 畫面總是跑掉，那肯定是因為你沒導入 Google 的 design.md","2026-06-27 12:00:00","7",{"url":624,"title":625,"date":626,"readingMinutes":639},"6",1784012757719]